While the majority of this pit has been eroded smooth, this pile of rock is ragged and haphazardly heaped. This may be the aftermath of a collapsed tunnel.

Worse, there doesn't appear to be any promising paths to continue on. Another route must be found to continue the ascent.
[OOC: This object is used by the Job system. Check the manual on the forum if you are unsure what to do with it.]

This rock face, though quite steep, has many crags and outcroppings that could be used to climb by a strong individual. Should you fall while climbing however only cold, unyielding stone awaits below...
